Lingua-Align version 0.01
=======================



INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DOCUMENTATION

Look at the files in doc/
To run on some small sample data: look at europarl/



DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

     XML::Parser



